# Stockli SEO

When editing public-facing routes or SEO files, follow `.cursor/skills/seo-agent/SKILL.md`.

- Use `lib/seo.ts` helpers (`buildPageMetadata`, JSON-LD builders).
- Keep private areas noindex; never blanket-noindex `app/(app)`.
- Keep guest browsing required for crawlable market pages in production.
- Canonical site: `https://mystockli.com`.
